Sender                               Receiver
  |                                      |
  |---- Frame 0 ---->                    |  (sending)
  |                                      |
  | <--- ACK 0 -----                     |  (received OK)
  |                                      |
  |---- Frame 1 ---->                    |
  |   (Frame 1 lost ❌ - random event)   |
  |         (wait TIMEOUT seconds...)    |
  |---- Frame 1 (retransmit) ---->       |
  | <--- ACK 1 -----                     |
  |                                      |
  |---- Frame 2 ---->                    |
  |                                      |
  | <--- ACK 2 lost ❌ (random event)    |
  |      (wait TIMEOUT seconds...)       |
  |---- Frame 2 (retransmit) ---->       |
  | <--- ACK 2 -----                     |
  |                                      |
  |---- Frame 3 ---->                    |
  | <--- ACK 3 -----                     |
